00415 void eol_keychain_write_hash(eolKeychain *link,eolFile *file)
00416 {
00417   GHashTableIter *iter = NULL;
00418   gpointer       *key = NULL;
00419   gpointer       *value = NULL;
00420   if (!link)return;
00421   if (link->keyType != eolKeychainHash)return;
00422   /*
00423   type
00424   count
00425   key
00426   value - expand for keychain type
00427   key
00428   value
00429   ...
00430   */
00431   eol_loader_write_uint_to_file(file,link->keyType);
00432   eol_loader_write_uint_to_file(file,link->itemCount);
00433   g_hash_table_iter_init(iter,link->keyValue);
00434   while(g_hash_table_iter_next(iter,key,value))
00435   {
00436     eol_loader_write_string_to_file(file,(char *)key);
00437     eol_keychain_write_link((eolKeychain *)value,file);
00438   }
00439 }

00441 void eol_keychain_write_line(eolKeychain *link,eolFile *file)

00466 void eol_keychain_write_link(eolKeychain *link,eolFile *file)
00467 {
00468   if ((!link) || (!file))return;
00469   switch(link->keyType)
00470   {
00471     case eolKeychainString:
00472       eol_keychain_write_string(link,file);
00473       break;
00474     case eolKeychainList:
00475       eol_keychain_write_hash(link,file);
00476       break;
00477     case eolKeychainHash:
00478     default:
00479       eol_logger_message(
00480         EOL_LOG_WARN,
00481         "eol_keychain:unsupported keychain type for writing: %i\n",
00482         link->keyType);
00483   }
00484 }
